313
00:17:19,747 --> 00:17:21,362
That's why they came by
my office earlier.

314
00:17:21,624 --> 00:17:22,830
To sign up for the showcase.

315
00:17:23,084 --> 00:17:26,247
Even sang a little song
to Vice Principal Luna and I.

316
00:17:26,504 --> 00:17:28,995
- They did?
- Yes.

317
00:17:29,257 --> 00:17:31,043
And we think having
a battle of the bands

318
00:17:31,300 --> 00:17:33,837
instead is
a marvelous idea.

319
00:17:41,394 --> 00:17:43,806
