(sighs)
None taken.

331
00:18:08,588 --> 00:18:09,748
Again.

332
00:18:10,006 --> 00:18:11,712
But that was when
Twilight was here.

333
00:18:11,966 --> 00:18:14,048
There may be some kind
of magic inside us,

334
00:18:14,302 --> 00:18:16,133
but it only comes out
when we play music.

335
00:18:16,387 --> 00:18:18,469
I sure don't know
how to use it

336
00:18:18,723 --> 00:18:22,307
to "whup anybody's butt."

337
00:18:22,560 --> 00:18:24,801
If only we could get
a message to Twilight.

338
00:18:25,062 --> 00:18:26,802
Maybe she could tell us
how to break the spell

339
00:18:27,064 --> 00:18:28,600
the Dazzlings have cast
on our friends.

340
00:18:28,858 --> 00:18:30,519
Well, that's not gonna happen.

341
00:18:30,776 --> 00:18:32,937
The porta|'s closed.

342
