cell phones where she's from.

345
00:18:41,162 --> 00:18:42,527
I may have an idea

346
00:18:42,788 --> 00:18:44,904
how we can get in touch
with Princess Twilight.

347
00:18:52,673 --> 00:18:55,506
When I was Princess Ce|estia's
student back in Equestria,

348
00:18:55,760 --> 00:18:58,467
she gave me this.

349
00:18:58,721 --> 00:19:01,588
Even after I abandoned my studies,
I held on to it.

350
00:19:01,849 --> 00:19:04,636
Deep down, I guess I knew
I was making a big mistake

351
00:19:04,894 --> 00:19:07,351
and I still wanted a way
to reach out to her.

352
00:19:10,066 --> 00:19:11,647
Maybe it still works.

353
00:19:11,901 --> 00:19:13,766
Rarity:
That's a book, darling.

354
00:19:14,028 --> 00:19:15,859
What do you mean
maybe still works?

355
00:19:16,113 --> 00:19:18,274
It used to be that
if I wrote something here,

356
00:19:18,532 --> 00:19:22,070
it would appear in the pages of a book
back in Princess Ce|estia's library.

357
00:19:22,328 --> 00:19:24,068
I get a message to her,

358
00:19:24,330 --> 00:19:26,821
then she can get a message
to Princess Twilight.

359
00:19:27,083 --> 00:19:30,075
So what are you waiting for?
Get to writing.

360
00:19:36,425 --> 00:19:38,006
Huh.

361
00:19:38,260 --> 00:19:41,047
Been a longtime since
I've written these words.

362
00:19:42,431 --> 00:19:45,138
"Dear Princess Ce|estia."

363
00:20:19,343 --> 00:20:21,174
Excuse me, Princess,

364
00:20:21,429 --> 00:20:22,885
where do you want all these
books from Princess Celestia?

365
00:20:23,139 --> 00:20:26,302
The library.
Third door on the left.

366
00:20:26,559 --> 00:20:29,141
Even this one that's glowing
and vibrating?

367
00:20:40,573 --> 00:20:41,904
What is it, Twilight?

368
00:20:42,158 --> 00:20:44,945
It looks like a message
to Princess Celestia

369
00:20:45,202 --> 00:20:46,658
from my friends
at Canterlot High.

370
00:20:46,912 --> 00:20:49,324
How is that even possible?

371
00:20:49,582 --> 00:20:50,662
I have no idea,

372
00:20:50,916 --> 00:20:53,749
but it sounds like
they need my help.

373
00:20:57,381 --> 00:20:58,996
The way Sunset Shimmer
described them,

374
00:20:59,258 --> 00:21:01,214
I think these new girls
sound an awful lot like

375
00:21:01,469 --> 00:21:03,755
the Sirens.

376
00:21:04,013 --> 00:21:05,844
Not the Sirens!

377
00:21:06,098 --> 00:21:09,181
I don't actually know
what that is.

378
00:21:09,435 --> 00:21:12,723
The Sirens were three beautiful
but dangerous creatures

379
00:21:12,980 --> 00:21:15,892
who had the power to charm
ponies with their music.

380
00:21:16,150 --> 00:21:17,686
But to maintain this power,

381
00:21:17,943 --> 00:21:20,980
they had to feed on the negativity
and distrust of others.

382
00:21:21,238 --> 00:21:23,775
The more of this
negative energy they consumed,

383
00:21:24,033 --> 00:21:26,115
the stronger
their voices became

384
00:21:26,368 --> 00:21:28,825
and the farther they could
spread their dark magic.

385
00:21:29,079 --> 00:21:31,536
I don't think I like
this story very much.

386
00:21:31,791 --> 00:21:33,782
Twilight:
If the Sirens had their way,

387
00:21:34,043 --> 00:21:36,409
they would have divided
and conquered all of Equestria.

388
00:21:36,670 --> 00:21:39,958
But a certain Star Swirl the Bearded
wasn't having it.

389
00:21:40,216 --> 00:21:43,959
Rumor has it he found a way
to banish them to another world.

390
00:21:44,220 --> 00:21:47,178
One where he believed
their magic power would be lost.

391
00:21:49,475 --> 00:21:52,387
That world must have been the one
where my Canterlot High friends live.

392
00:21:52,645 --> 00:21:55,557
But Star Swirl must have
sent them there ages ago.

393
00:21:55,815 --> 00:21:57,646
How come they're
just surfacing now?

394
00:21:57,900 --> 00:21:59,891
I don't know,
but if my hunch is right

395
00:22:00,152 --> 00:22:02,518
and it is the Sirens
who have come to Canterlot High,

396
00:22:02,780 --> 00:22:05,396
