Okay, first of all, if there was bubble
blowing going on,

402
00:22:19,338 --> 00:22:20,794
why wasn't I told about it?

403
00:22:21,048 --> 00:22:24,165
And secondly, if the connection
is totally cut off,

404
00:22:24,426 --> 00:22:27,839
how was Sunset Shimmer
able to get a message to Twilight?

405
00:22:28,097 --> 00:22:31,715
( gasps )
Pinkie, you're a genius.

406
00:22:31,976 --> 00:22:33,591
Yeah, I get that a lot.

407
00:22:33,853 --> 00:22:35,639
Now about those bubbles.

408
00:22:49,994 --> 00:22:52,030
Twilight: ...and the interval between
the two points is defined

409
00:22:52,288 --> 00:22:54,199
