from here to there.

415
00:23:09,555 --> 00:23:11,511
There to here.
Here-there.

416
00:23:11,765 --> 00:23:15,053
- There to here. Here to there. There--
- We get the idea.

417
00:23:17,146 --> 00:23:19,432
Now to see
if it actually works.

418
00:23:31,452 --> 00:23:33,659
All: Ooh.

419
00:23:58,687 --> 00:24:00,769
All: Ahh.

420
00:24:01,023 --> 00:24:03,981
Don't suppose we could
join you this time around?

421
00:24:04,234 --> 00:24:05,565
Better not.

422
00:24:05,819 --> 00:24:07,525
It could make things
pretty confusing if Canterlot High

423
00:24:07,780 --> 00:24:10,021
