at Canterlot High.

427
00:24:17,122 --> 00:24:19,488
And you never know when you might
need your trusty assistant.

428
00:24:19,750 --> 00:24:23,584
- Mm-hmm.
- Yes!

429
00:24:23,837 --> 00:24:25,418
We won't be gone long.

430
00:24:25,673 --> 00:24:27,755
( overlapping chatter)

431
00:24:28,008 --> 00:24:29,919
And don't forget
to dress well.

432
00:24:33,597 --> 00:24:36,088
Ready, Spike?

433
00:24:37,226 --> 00:24:38,591
Ready.

434
00:25:03,502 --> 00:25:06,915
(sighs) I'm starting to think
she's not coming.

435
00:25:08,882 --> 00:25:10,167
All:
Twilight!

436
00:25:10,426 --> 00:25:13,463
Ooh. I'm back.

437
00:25:21,270 --> 00:25:23,761
