remained here at Canterlot High.

466
00:26:41,433 --> 00:26:42,923
Now that we're
all back together,

467
00:26:43,185 --> 00:26:44,891
we can use that magic
on the Sirens.

468
00:26:45,145 --> 00:26:47,101
Just like when we were able to use it
on Sunset Shimmer

469
00:26:47,356 --> 00:26:51,099
when she turned into
that horrifyingly awful winged monster.

470
00:26:51,360 --> 00:26:52,475
No offense.

471
00:26:52,736 --> 00:26:54,852
None taken.

472
00:26:55,114 --> 00:26:56,650
