the better.

479
00:27:13,757 --> 00:27:15,748
Any idea where
the Dazzlings might be?

480
00:27:18,595 --> 00:27:21,382
(slurps)
Ahh.

481
00:27:21,640 --> 00:27:23,050
There's a big party tonight
for all the bands

482
00:27:23,308 --> 00:27:24,593
who signed up
to be in the showcase.

483
00:27:24,852 --> 00:27:26,592
That would include
the Dazzlings.

484
00:27:29,690 --> 00:27:31,976
Looks like we've got
a party to crash.

485
00:27:33,652 --> 00:27:35,608
( chatter)

486
00:27:48,834 --> 00:27:50,950
(sighs)
I'm gonna get more punch.

487
00:27:53,297 --> 00:27:54,833
Twilight?

488
00:27:55,090 --> 00:27:57,081
Oh, bumped into--

489
00:27:57,342 --> 00:27:58,798
always doing...

490
00:27:59,052 --> 00:28:00,792
What are you doing here?

491
00:28:01,054 --> 00:28:03,215
You came back for
the big competition, right?

492
00:28:03,473 --> 00:28:05,134
Something like that.

493
00:28:05,392 --> 00:28:07,758
Not that there's going to be
any real competition.

494
00:28:08,020 --> 00:28:11,057
No one here wants this
as bad as my band does.

495
00:28:21,700 --> 00:28:23,907
( chatter)

496
00:28:25,078 --> 00:28:27,160
Can you excuse me
forjust a minute?

497
00:28:38,175 --> 00:28:40,131
( overlapping conversations )

498
00:28:45,140 --> 00:28:48,132
