Oh, no. No one's mingling.

499
00:28:48,393 --> 00:28:51,100
It's like there's some kind
of underlying tension

500
00:28:51,355 --> 00:28:53,437
that could bubble
to the surface at any minute.

501
00:28:53,690 --> 00:28:54,975
It's the fruit punch,
isn't it?

502
00:28:55,234 --> 00:28:57,099
I knew I used
too much grape juice.

503
00:28:57,361 --> 00:28:59,977
It's not the fruit punch,
it's us.

504
00:29:00,239 --> 00:29:02,446
But the punch is awful, too.

505
00:29:02,699 --> 00:29:04,860
What do you know
about good fruit punch?

506
00:29:05,118 --> 00:29:06,278
More than you.

507
00:29:06,536 --> 00:29:08,492
- Do not.
- Do, too.

508
00:29:08,747 --> 00:29:11,159
This is just
the kickoff party, girls.

509
00:29:11,416 --> 00:29:13,281
Imagine what a tizzy
